{"name":"Концентрация фанатика","type":"feat","system":{"description":{"value":"<p><em>6-й уровень, умение пути фанатика</em></p><p>Божественная сила, что питает вашу ярость, может защитить вас от вреда. Если вы провалили спасбросок, пребывая в @Compendium[world.umeniya-phantom.R4K0A3uRAOkQL45q]{ярости}, вы можете перебросить его и будете обязаны использовать новое значение.</p><p>Вы можете использовать это способность только <strong>один</strong> раз в течение одной ярости.</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"XGE","activation":{"type":"","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":null,"max":"","per":null,"recovery":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":"","actionType":"other","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":""},"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"flat"},"requirements":"Barbarian 6 (Zealot)","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"img":"icons/magic/perception/eye-ringed-glow-angry-red.webp","flags":{"plutonium":{"page":"subclassFeature","source":"XGE","hash":"fanatical%20focus_barbarian_phb_zealot_xge_6_xge","propDroppable":"subclassFeature"}},"effects":[],"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"2.0.3","coreVersion":"10.290","createdTime":1668296746178,"modifiedTime":1668301294668,"lastModifiedBy":"XfGBpRnEldwS51r8"},"_id":"RAHIV3j3bQ2Wecjk","folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"XfGBpRnEldwS51r8":3}}
